h3 Shopping List

table.table
  tr
    th Award
    th.numeric Quantity

  tr.section-heading
    td(colspan="10") Ranks
  - @unit.achievements.unawarded.ranks.order('ordinal').group_by(&:name).each do |name, achievements|
    tr
      td = name
      td.numeric = achievements.count

  tr.section-heading
    td(colspan="10") Merit Badges
  - @unit.achievements.unawarded.merit_badges.order('name').group_by(&:name).each do |name, achievements|
    tr
      td = name
      td.numeric = achievements.count
